item.title: 9-1-1: Lone Star
item.description: 9-1-1: Lone Star is an American procedural drama television series that follows the lives of Austin, Texas's first responders. It was created for Fox by Ryan Murphy, Brad Falchuk, and Tim Minear. The series is a spin-off of the American procedural drama television series 9-1-1, and was ordered by Fox in May 2019. The series premiered on January 19, 2020. In May 2023, the series was renewed for a fifth and final season, which premiered on September 23, 2024 and will end on February 3, 2025.
